               EM     
               SM Inlines     
                GO     
                 SM x:_Items     [Implicit]     
                  V "In the last five years, researchers in Computer Animation have proved that only physics-based animation laws may efficiently simulate the laws of nature. Almost all natural phenomena can be modelted with differential equations. Now the question is: how to find suitablte models and stablte and efficient numerical methods for solving the equations."     
                 EM     
